data.description: Great VIEWS and lots of OPEN SPACE! Welcome to this early 70's era patio home. The interior with lots of custom finishes including wood flooring has two steps down into the living room adding that mid-century style layout. This is a well maintained property with a new foam roof and patio cover in 2020. The master bath opens to a patio off of the front of the home with an outdoor shower. Great for rinsing off after the pool. The home sits on the north side of Oak with incredible views of Papago Park and never ending sunrise & sunset views. The home is centrally located in South Scottsdale just minutes from the Desert Botanical Gardens, Old Town Scottsdale, the Phoenix Zoo and Phoenix Sky Harbor. Excellent location! As an added bonus Heritage East is 10 acres of a park like setting o mature trees and grass.
